annotationA: WHAMM and JMY related, isoform B; GTPase binding; actin binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: microtubule bundle formation; actin cytoskeleton organization
annotationB: Verprolin 1, isoform G; Verprolin 1 (Vrp1) is the sole Drosophila homolog of the conserved Verprolin/WASp-Interacting-Protein family of actin regulators. Vrp1 facilitates myoblast fusion in somatic muscles by recruiting the branched-actin polymerization machinery to sites of myoblast-myotube attachment and fusion
